<!-- Definition and symptoms -->

'''陣發性室上性心搏過速'''（{{lang-en|Paroxysmal supraventricular tachycardia，簡稱 '''PSVT'''）}}是[[室上性心搏過速|室上性心搏過速]]中的一種<ref name=NIH2011Type>{{cite web|title=Types of Arrhythmia|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/arr/types|website=NHLBI|date=July 1, 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150607165144/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/arr/types|archivedate=2015-06-07|df=|access-date=2017-08-08}}</ref>。一般患者不會出現症狀<ref name=Fer2012>{{cite book|last1=Ferri|first1=Fred F.|title=Ferri's Clinical Advisor 2013,5 Books in 1, Expert Consult - Online and Print,1: Ferri's Clinical Advisor 2013|date=2012|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=978-0323083737|page=807|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=OR3VERnvzzEC&pg=PA807|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002093207/https://books.google.ca/books?id=OR3VERnvzzEC&pg=PA807|archivedate=2016-10-02|df=}}</ref>，若有則可能是[[心悸|心悸]]、頭重腳輕、盜汗、[[呼吸困难|呼吸困难]]及[[胸痛|胸痛]]<ref name=NIH2011Syn>{{cite web|title=What Are the Signs and Symptoms of an Arrhythmia?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/arr/signs|website=NHLBI|accessdate=27 September 2016|date=July 1, 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219081446/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/arr/signs|archivedate=2015-02-19|df=}}</ref>，症狀出現得快，也消失得快<ref name=Al2016>{{cite journal|last1=Al-Zaiti|first1=SS|last2=Magdic|first2=KS|title=Paroxysmal Supraventricular Tachycardia: Pathophysiology, Diagnosis, and Management.|journal=Critical Care Nursing Clinics of North America|date=September 2016|volume=28|issue=3|pages=309–16|pmid=27484659|doi=10.1016/j.cnc.2016.04.005}}</ref>。

<!-- Cause and diagnosis -->
病因尚屬未知<ref name=Al2016/>，風險因子有酒精、[[咖啡因|咖啡因]]、[[尼古丁|尼古丁]]、[[心理壓力|心理壓力]]及遺傳得來的[[沃夫巴金森懷特症候群|沃夫巴金森懷特症候群]]<ref name=Al2016/>。此疾病的機制和{{link-en|副传导路径|accessory pathway}}有關，會造成進入錯誤迴路（{{lang-en|re-entry}}）的[[心律不整|心律不整]]<ref name=Al2016/>。診斷會藉由[[心电图|心电图]]（{{lang-en|ECG}}）來進行，若有{{link-en|窄QRS波群|narrow QRS complexes}}且心律較快，在每分鐘150至240下之間，即可確診為陣發性室上性心搏過速<ref name=Al2016/>。

<!-- Treatment and prevention -->
常見的初步治療為採用{{le|迷走神經刺激術|Vagal maneuver}}，例如{{le|持續閉氣用力|Valsalva maneuver}}（又稱伐氏操作），如果不見效且患者[[血壓|血壓]]正常，可能會採用[[腺苷|腺苷]]；如果腺苷沒有幫助，可能會採用[[鈣離子通道阻滯劑|鈣離子通道阻滯劑]]或[[β受體阻滯劑|β受體阻滯劑]]；或者會改採[[心率調整|心率調整]]來治療<ref name=AHA2015>{{cite journal|last1=Neumar|first1=RW|last2=Shuster|first2=M|last3=Callaway|first3=CW|last4=Gent|first4=LM|last5=Atkins|first5=DL|last6=Bhanji|first6=F|last7=Brooks|first7=SC|last8=de Caen|first8=AR|last9=Donnino|first9=MW|last10=Ferrer|first10=JM|last11=Kleinman|first11=ME|last12=Kronick|first12=SL|last13=Lavonas|first13=EJ|last14=Link|first14=MS|last15=Mancini|first15=ME|last16=Morrison|first16=LJ|last17=O'Connor|first17=RE|last18=Samson|first18=RA|last19=Schexnayder|first19=SM|last20=Singletary|first20=EM|last21=Sinz|first21=EH|last22=Travers|first22=AH|last23=Wyckoff|first23=MH|last24=Hazinski|first24=MF|title=Part 1: Executive Summary: 2015 American Heart Association Guidelines Update for Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation and Emergency Cardiovascular Care.|journal=Circulation|date=3 November 2015|volume=132|issue=18 Suppl 2|pages=S315–67|pmid=26472989|doi=10.1161/cir.0000000000000252}}</ref>。預防之後發作的方法是{{le|心導管燒灼術|Catheter ablation}}<ref name=Al2016/>。

<!-- Epidemiology and prognosis -->
在每千人中約有2.3人患有陣發性室上性心搏過速<ref name=Kat2016>{{cite book|last1=Katritsis|first1=Demosthenes G.|last2=Camm|first2=A. John|last3=Gersh|first3=Bernard J.|title=Clinical Cardiology: Current Practice Guidelines|date=2016|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=9780198733324|page=538|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=VX7ADAAAQBAJ&pg=PA538|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002094014/https://books.google.ca/books?id=VX7ADAAAQBAJ&pg=PA538|archivedate=2016-10-02|df=}}</ref>，通常發病於12~45歲<ref name=Al2016/><ref name=Kat2016/>，女性患者較男性患者為多<ref name=Al2016/>。[[心臟|心臟]]健全者的治療成效往往也很好<ref name=Al2016/>。在釐清心臟病症時，可能會藉由[[心臟超音波|心臟超音波]]來做判斷<ref name=Fer2012/>。

